At that time Jesus said, "I thank you, Father, Lord of heaven and earth, because you have hidden these things from the wise and intelligent and have revealed them to infants."
Yes, Father. This is what I wanted.
The father gave me everything. The father is the only one who knows the son. And the only ones who know the father are the son and those whom the son chooses to make him known.
